{"tid":715082,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯首2場跑動距離32隊之冠 美國反禁藥組織認為不尋常","createTime":"2018-06-24T07:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T20:31:55.000Z","uid":55981,"like":108,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"8904d6b80790930eeb2d35be3f27e85ed5503f5a","tid":715082,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:44:09.000Z","msg":"世界盃東道主俄羅斯繼上周四（14日）在揭幕戰大勝沙特阿拉伯5:0後，在周二（19日）再下一城以3:1擊退由沙拿領軍的埃及。<br />\n<br />\n決賽周32隊之中，俄羅斯為世界排名最低的隊伍。他們卻能踢出如此出色的表現，引來美國反禁藥組織（US Anti-Doping Agency）行政總裁提出，要求俄羅斯球員接受更多禁藥測試。俄羅斯隊醫反駁指，球隊今年已提交超過300次測試結果，全部均顯示球員未有服用禁藥。<br />\n<br />\n美國反禁藥組織行政總裁泰加特（Travis Tygart）周四（21日）向英國《每日電訊報》（The Daily Telegraph）表示，國際足協（FIFA）應該加緊要求俄羅斯接受禁藥測試：「（他們）出色的表現需要額外測試。」泰加特過去曾指出，俄羅斯根本不應該獲得世界盃主辦權。<br />\n<br />\n今屆世界盃，俄羅斯除了已經取得兩連勝，球員在對上兩場比賽的跑動距離，都比其餘隊伍多。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯隊醫別祖格洛夫（Eduard Bezuglov）反駁指，球隊今年已向FIFA和歐洲足協（UEFA）提交超過300次測試結果，全部均顯示球員未有服用禁藥。他更稱，敢打賭俄羅斯提交樣本的次數一定比英格蘭更頻密。<br />\n<br />\n國際足協拒絕公開俄羅斯球員禁藥測試資料，並稱他們不能評論有關測試。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯運動員屢次捲入禁藥風波，2016年5月，俄羅斯前反禁藥主管更公開承認，俄羅斯在2014年索契冬奧期間，當局不止有系統地向運動員供應類固醇，並協助掩飾藥檢結果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/202751/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E8%B7%91%E5%8B%95%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A-%E5%8F%8D%E7%A6%81%E8%97%A5%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E4%BF%83%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E8%97%A5%E6%AA%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F202751%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%259B%2583-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%25B7%2591%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25B7%259D%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A-%25E5%258F%258D%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2597%25A5%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%2597%25A5%25E6%25AA%25A2&d=8qpNhUi%2BzyL8RemxCRsfKk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e1038b78\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/202751/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E8%B7%91%E5%8B%95%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A-%E5%8F%8D%E7%A6%81%E8%97%A5%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E4%BF%83%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E8%97%A5%E6%AA%A2</a>"},{"pid":"4b5af393e1bbc462f58ca2a1c8100993130bc202","tid":715082,"uid":55981,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:44:44.000Z","msg":"Ian DW@sportdw<br />\n<br />\nMore of a breakdown of the distance covered stats for the World Cup so far. Russia covering more distance, generally at faster speeds and completing more sprints than any other team so far...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DgNZGsKWAAI4XYc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDgNZGsKWAAI4XYc.jpg&h=fd564b5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79feaabd4385308bf320628e738d2cf7f9ebe57e","tid":715082,"uid":132587,"like":222,"dislike":6,"score":216,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"俄狗不嬲作風 冰壺都食禁藥 唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b36fd038b129bd8f1eb9996e05fe8f833a98e70","tid":715082,"uid":61257,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:46:54.000Z","msg":"小花隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8150266dd812833bc201b60a2102d501563214","tid":715082,"uid":186181,"like":172,"dislike":2,"score":170,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:46:55.000Z","msg":"有睇就知<br />\n真係跑得仲癲過利記<br />\n高速率跑足全場..."},{"pid":"d3811e4fcb1e23db57bd326b23c9ddff78c2a7ae","tid":715082,"uid":55981,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DgNwPmcW0AI5etP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDgNwPmcW0AI5etP.jpg&h=4232cbc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIan DW@sportdw<br />\n<br />\nFor a bit of reference, here are the distances covered, breakdown by speed and sprints per match from the 2014 World Cup..."},{"pid":"8c5df524d4a9afd66acc9603a9054d4715563ccf","tid":715082,"uid":74918,"like":82,"dislike":2,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:47:58.000Z","msg":"當戰鬥民族流㗎<br />\n美中不足就屈鳩俄佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">大佬呀<br />\n開飯都靠佢地下場㗎啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"6bce4f4481730644fcdff06fe052655eb751da5f","tid":715082,"uid":31151,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:48:20.000Z","msg":"屌 俄佬班球員就算逐個睇番踢聯賽都係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4280b1b9d48bcd8cfa0f1305bae42bc5f325ea65","tid":715082,"uid":89931,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"散步廷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66975eec41a2179ceac8c8fb1db47e51d78fa258","tid":715082,"uid":187916,"like":54,"dislike":3,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:50:40.000Z","msg":"俄佬出撚晒名食禁藥 咩運動都係"},{"pid":"4e8bae44cce8601ee529168fe35afa8ec0899c98","tid":715082,"uid":6435,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"阿根廷班爛坦真係散步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2887e4451e3a91624f32c8d602aa597aaa22ef37","tid":715082,"uid":100689,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4280b1b9d48bcd8cfa0f1305bae42bc5f325ea65","tid":715082,"uid":89931,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"散步廷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:52:03.000Z","msg":"葡提子都跑好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ba19e49117fb5e2d15c2eab39d43c0459f515e","tid":715082,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-2